## How Fast Can I Get a Zambia e-Visa?

Zambiaâ€™s e-Visa system is efficient, but processing times can vary.

## Typical Processing Time

The official processing time is **3-5 working days**. Delays may occur during peak periods.

## Expedited Options

Zambia does not offer official expedited processing. Apply early to avoid issues.

## Tips for Fast Approval

- Apply at least 7 days before travel
- Double-check your documents
- Avoid public holidays

## What to Do If Delayed

Contact Zambia Immigration or check your application status online.

## FAQ

- **Can I apply on weekends?** Yes, but processing is on working days.
- **Can I extend my e-Visa?** Extensions may be possible; check with immigration.